{"tid":1850253,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"小S支那年撈1.53億 「可買3064萬個口罩」","createTime":"2020-01-29T12:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T12:59:27.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd96d27078a2d53b2e8c3e17f5479108f2136865","tid":1850253,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pfx71xa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpfx71xa.jpg&h=e2db8365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國武漢肺炎疫情肆虐，台灣也遭入侵，目前口罩禁止出口，女星小S在中國平台微博罵「若不互相幫助，不是人類該有的行為吧！恨，比病毒更可怕」，網友為此以小S年收做基底，算出：「一共可買3064萬個口罩」。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gcwD8bG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgcwD8bG.jpg&h=133d85ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小S這些年在中國主持不少節目，目前手上還與蔡康永錄《真相吧！花花萬物》，曾上新聞一年在中國賺達1億5320萬台幣，而大S在中國也收入頗豐，日前她已在日本掃1萬個口罩送武漢救援，若一個醫療口罩5元，以小S年收換算，網友發現小S可買3064萬個口罩，數量非常驚人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxYbJLb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxYbJLb.jpg&h=48b3c6da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7aa0c6368ae42465bbf4e2a6aa6a1fe3f722d87","tid":1850253,"uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDkp3LL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDkp3LL.jpg&h=24f416b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37d800c20f2ccf15035c23eba6ec445d270c7a2","tid":1850253,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGE6unr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGE6unr.jpg&h=1849f916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx